# --- Backend (.NET) Engellenecekler ---
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/.vs/
**/*.user
**/appsettings.Development.json

# --- Frontend (Node/React) Engellenecekler ---
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.env

# --- AI / Python Engellenecekler ---
**/__pycache__/
**/venv/
**/.venv/